ZH: 我们明天下午三点集合在学校门口。
EN: We will gather at the school gate tomorrow afternoon at 3 o'clock.

ZH: 请大家准时集合在会议室。
EN: Please gather in the conference room on time.

ZH: 马上集合，我们要出发了！
EN: Gather up quickly, we are about to set off!

ZH: 学校全体师生被要求在操场集合。
EN: All teachers and students are required to gather on the playground.

ZH: 昨天晚上，我们在朋友家集合过聚餐。
EN: We gathered at a friend's house for dinner last night.

ZH: 请把表演队员集合起来，我们要开始排练了。
EN: Gather the performers together, we are about to start rehearsing.

ZH: 大家集合的地方是在火车站前面的广场。
EN: The gathering place is in front of the train station square.

ZH: 请按照指示集合在指定的地点。
EN: Please gather at the designated location according to the instructions.

ZH: 星期六我们将在公园集合办一次野餐。
EN: We will gather for a picnic in the park on Saturday.

ZH: 大家都迟到了，凭什么要我等你们集合？
EN: Everyone was late, why should I wait for you to gather?

ZH: 我们必须在一个小时内集合起来，否则会错过火车。
EN: We must gather within one hour, otherwise we will miss the train.

ZH: 昨天晚上举行了一个家庭聚会，亲戚们都集合在一起。
EN: There was a family gathering last night, and relatives gathered together.

ZH: 春节期间，全家人会集合在一起过年。
EN: During the Spring Festival, the whole family gathers together to celebrate.

ZH: 我的老乡们集合起来，为家乡的发展贡献力量。
EN: My fellow townsmen gather together to contribute to the development of our hometown.

ZH: 公司要求所有员工集合在大厅参加培训。
EN: The company requires all employees to gather in the hall for training.

ZH: 请大家按照队长的指示集合起来。
EN: Please gather together according to the captain's instructions.

ZH: 这里有一个集合点，我们可以在这里等待救援。
EN: There is a gathering point here where we can wait for rescue.

ZH: 星期五晚上我们要去夜市集合。
EN: We will gather at the night market on Friday evening.

ZH: 大家快点集合，我们要开始下一项活动了。
EN: Hurry up and gather everyone, we are about to start the next activity.

ZH: 这个健身俱乐部是为喜欢集体锻炼的人群而设的。
EN: This fitness club is designed for people who enjoy group exercise.
